[Perhaps Sierra Leonean doctors working overseas (10 in the UK alone) should apply for leave to return and help?

I can imagine much confusion resulting from giving a new drug a name similar to an existing drug -- especially in the harried environment of an Ebola ward, and also over the phone from journalists. - Mod.JW]

